atarça</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%BE%D0%BB_%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%BB%D0%BC%D0%B0%D1%82%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80" title="Сол Перлматтер — ukrainien" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ur"><a href="https://ur.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%84_%D9%BE%D8%B1%D9%84%D9%85%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%B1" title="ساول پرلموتر — ourdou" lang="ur" hreflang="ur" class="interlanguage-link-target">اردو</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saul_Perlmutter" title="Saul Perlmutter — vietnamien" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-wuu"><a href="https://wuu.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E7%8F%80%E5%B0%94%E9%A9%AC%E7%89%B9" title="索尔·珀尔马特 — wu" lang="wuu" hreflang="wuu" class="interlanguage-link-target">吴语</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-yo"><a href="https://yo.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saul_Perlmutter" title="Saul Perlmutter — yoruba" lang="yo" hreflang="yo" class="interlanguage-link-target">Yorùbá</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-za"><a href="https://za.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saul_Perlmutter" title="Saul Perlmutter — zhuang" lang="za" hreflang="za" class="interlanguage-link-target">Vahcuengh</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E7%8F%80%E5%B0%94%E9%A9%AC%E7%89%B9" title="索尔·珀尔马特 — chinois" lang="zh" hreflang="zh" class="interlanguage-link-target">中文</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh-yue"><a href="https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%A2%E7%BE%85%E7%8F%80%E7%88%BE%E7%A9%86%E7%89%B9" title="索羅珀爾穆特 — Cantonese" lang="yue" hreflang="yue" class="interlanguage-link-target">粵語</a></li></ul>
