		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="fr" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="infobox infobox_v3 large"><div class="entete defaut" style="background-color:#EEEEFF;color:#000000"><div>Saul Perlmutter</div></div><div><div class="images" style="padding:2px 0"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Saul_Perlmutter.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Image dans Infobox." src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/72/Saul_Perlmutter.jpg" decoding="async" width="198" height="334" data-file-width="198" data-file-height="334" /></a></div><div class="legend">Saul Perlmutter recevant le <a href="/wiki/Prix_Shaw" title="Prix Shaw">prix Shaw d'astronomie</a> en 2006.</div></div><table><caption style="color:#000000;text-align:center;background-color:#EEEEFF">Biographie</caption><tbody><tr class=""><th scope="row">Naissance</th><td class=""><div>
